            <title>数码暴龙机复刻彩色版，可 USB 充电明年 2 月发售</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/03/bandai-spirits/hottopic/spotlight/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=bandai-spirits</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/03/bandai-spirits/hottopic/spotlight/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[毛]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 10:41:05 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[城中热话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[玩具]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[BANDAI SPIRITS]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[数码暴龙机]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1197069</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>BANDAI SPIRITS 昨（2 日）宣布为纪念训练游戏「数码暴龙机」发售 25 周年，表示将推出「数码暴龙机 COLOR」（デジモンペンデュラムCOLOR）。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-03-18.00.53-scaled.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197080" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-03-18.00.53-694x339.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="339" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-03-18.00.53-694x339.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-03-18.00.53-1280x625.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-03-18.00.53-768x375.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-03-18.00.53-1536x750.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-03-18.00.53-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>新版本的「数码暴龙机 COLOR」为旧版数码暴龙机的复刻产品，并采用全新的彩色液晶画面及 Type-C 充电器，以及将数码暴龙机过往的摆锤更换为加速度感知器。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1197071" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/006.jpg" alt="" width="512" height="512" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/006.jpg 512w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/006-120x120.jpg 120w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 512px" /></p><p>新款机身共三款颜色，分别为 NATURE SPIRITS（原版银蓝色）、DEEP SAVERS（原版蓝橙）及 NIGHTMARE SOLDIERS（原版红黑色）。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_33400"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/v_rbNKb4JBI?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;controls=1&#038;color=white&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;rel=0&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>同时，官方本次的宣传亦再现了当年的广告宣传影片，复刻的当年泳手配合广告歌六音乐跳舞的画面。</p><p>「数码暴龙机 COLOR」的价格为 7150 日元（约港币 $373 元），即日起开放预订至 11 月 2 日。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.4gamer.net/games/664/G066461/20231002012/">4gamer</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
            </description>
